[
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> would have <st data-num=\"0539\" class=\"\">believed</st><n id=\"1\" /> what we<n id=\"2\" /> just <st data-num=\"08052\" class=\"\">heard</st>?<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 04310\">When</st><n id=\"4\" /> was the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"02220\" class=\"\">power</st><n id=\"5\" /> <st data-num=\"01540\" class=\"\">revealed</st> through him?</p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">sprouted up</st> like a <st data-num=\"03126\" class=\"\">twig</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> God,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">like a <st data-num=\"08328\" class=\"\">root</st> out of <st data-num=\"06723\" class=\"\">parched</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">soil</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he had <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> stately <st data-num=\"08389\" class=\"\">form</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"01926\" class=\"\">majesty</st> that might <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">catch</st> our <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">attention</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> special <st data-num=\"04758\" class=\"\">appearance</st> that we should <st data-num=\"02530\" class=\"\">want</st> to follow him.<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He was <st data-num=\"0959\" class=\"\">despised</st> and <st data-num=\"02310\" class=\"\">rejected</st> by <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">people</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> who experienced <st data-num=\"04341\" class=\"\">pain</st> and was <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">acquainted</st> with <st data-num=\"02483\" class=\"\">illness</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">people <st data-num=\"04564\" class=\"\">hid</st> their <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">faces</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> him;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he was <st data-num=\"0959\" class=\"\">despised</st>, and we <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">considered</st> him <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">insignificant</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0403\" class=\"\">But</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">lifted up</st> our <st data-num=\"02483\" class=\"\">illnesses</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"05445\" class=\"\">carried</st> our <st data-num=\"04341\" class=\"\">pain</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">even though <st data-num=\"0587\" class=\"\">we</st> <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">thought</st> he was being <st data-num=\"05060\" class=\"\">punished</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">attacked</st> by <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, and <st data-num=\"06031\" class=\"\">afflicted</st> for something he had done.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">He</st> was <st data-num=\"02490\" class=\"\">wounded</st> because of<n id=\"1\" /> our <st data-num=\"06588\" class=\"\">rebellious deeds</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01792\" class=\"\">crushed</st> because of our <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sins</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">endured</st> <st data-num=\"04148\" class=\"\">punishment</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">that made</st> us <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">well</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">because of his <st data-num=\"02250\" class=\"\">wounds</st> we have been <st data-num=\"07495\" class=\"\">healed</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> of us had <st data-num=\"08582\" class=\"\">wandered off</st> like <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">sheep</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">each</st> of us had <st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">strayed off</st> on his own <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">path</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> caused the <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sin</st> of <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of us to <st data-num=\"06293\" class=\"\">attack</st> him.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">He</st> was <st data-num=\"05065\" class=\"\">treated harshly</st> and <st data-num=\"06031\" class=\"\">afflicted</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but he did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> even <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">open</st> his <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Like a <st data-num=\"07716\" class=\"\">lamb</st> <st data-num=\"02986\" class=\"\">led</st> to the <st data-num=\"02874\" class=\"\">slaughtering</st> block,<p class=\"poetry\">like a <st data-num=\"07353\" class=\"\">sheep</st> <st data-num=\"0481\" class=\"\">silent</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> her <st data-num=\"01494\" class=\"\">shearers</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">he did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> even <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">open</st> his <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He was <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">led away</st> after an <st data-num=\"06115\" class=\"\">unjust</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">trial</st><n id=\"1\" />\u2014<p class=\"poetry\">but <st data-num=\"01755 04310 \">who</st> even <st data-num=\"07878\" class=\"\">cared</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, he was <st data-num=\"01504\" class=\"\">cut off</st> from the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of the <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">living</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">because of the <st data-num=\"06588\" class=\"\">rebellion</st> of his own<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> he was <st data-num=\"05061\" class=\"\">wounded</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">intended</st> to <st data-num=\"06913\" class=\"\">bury</st> him <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">criminals</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but he ended up <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">in</st> a <st data-num=\"06223\" class=\"\">rich man\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">tomb</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">because</st><n id=\"3\" /> he had <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">committed</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"02555\" class=\"\">violent deeds</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">nor</st> had he <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">spoken</st> <st data-num=\"04820\" class=\"\">deceitfully</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Though the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"02654\" class=\"\">desired</st> to <st data-num=\"01792\" class=\"\">crush</st> him and <st data-num=\"02470\" class=\"\">make</st> him <st data-num=\"02470\" class=\"\">ill</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">once</st> <st data-num=\"0817\" class=\"\">restitution</st> is <st data-num=\"07760 05315\">made</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> <st data-num=\"02233\" class=\"\">descendants</st> and <st data-num=\"0748\" class=\"\">enjoy long</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">life</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"02656\" class=\"\">purpose</st> will be <st data-num=\"06743\" class=\"\">accomplished</st> through <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">him</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Having <st data-num=\"05999 05315\">suffered</st>, he will <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">reflect on</st> his work,<p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">be satisfied</st> when he <st data-num=\"01847\" class=\"\">understands</st> what he has done.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cMy <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"06663\" class=\"\">acquit</st> <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">many</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">for <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"05445\" class=\"\">carried</st> their <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sins</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "53",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">So</st> I will <st data-num=\"02505\" class=\"\">assign</st> him <st data-num=\"02505\" class=\"\">a portion</st> with the <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">multitudes</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"02505\" class=\"\">divide</st> the <st data-num=\"07998\">spoils of victory</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> the <st data-num=\"06099\" class=\"\">powerful</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08478 0834\">because</st> he <st data-num=\"06168 05315\">willingly submitted</st><n id=\"3\" /> to <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">death</st><p class=\"poetry\">and was <st data-num=\"04487\" class=\"\">numbered</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> the <st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">rebels</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">when <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">lifted up</st> the <st data-num=\"02399\" class=\"\">sin</st> of <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">many</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06293\" class=\"\">intervened</st><n id=\"4\" /> on behalf of the <st data-num=\"06586\" class=\"\">rebels</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  }
]